rComments: This prof is awesome. Cares a lot about her students and gives excellent feedback. Recommended.

No doubt one of the best, most helpful professor in design Studio III at Ryerson University. I had a great time, she gives amazing feedback. Though a lot of work but grade tells the truth. One of the only professors in DAS who allow you to be more trying-some in your design.
it has been a pleasure having her as a studio professor for both my second year studio courses. On the whole it was a great learning experience.
Really nice and approachable. Helpful comments with constructive criticism. Highly recommended for undergrad studio.

studio courses will never be easy. however a helpful prof will make the experience that much more bearable. she was rather nice and wasn't harsh when criticizing, which sometimes make the final marks rather surprising. she was lenient and understanding when it came to penalty for lateness. u have to be wiling to put the effort into studio courses.
